WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.333 --> 00:00:02.600
The current predicament of the Jiang family is not caused by me at all

2
00:00:02.600 --> 00:00:03.800
You don't have to come and beg me

3
00:00:03.800 --> 00:00:06.100
Guanghua Bank acquired by your Huacan Group

4
00:00:06.100 --> 00:00:07.900
Freeze all assets of the Jiang family

5
00:00:08.100 --> 00:00:09.600
If it can't be thawed tomorrow

6
00:00:09.966 --> 00:00:11.200
The Jiang family has no funds to return

7
00:00:11.200 --> 00:00:12.800
Will declare bankruptcy

8
00:00:12.900 --> 00:00:15.266
Guanghua Bank freezes the assets of your Jiang family

9
00:00:15.300 --> 00:00:16.700
Well, he has a point.

10
00:00:16.766 --> 00:00:18.566
If you really want to save the Jiang family

11
00:00:18.566 --> 00:00:20.100
Then you should go to Guanghua Bank.

12
00:00:20.100 --> 00:00:22.266
Instead of making a fuss here

13
00:00:22.333 --> 00:00:24.500
But Guanghua Bank listens to you

14
00:00:24.500 --> 00:00:26.000
As long as you say a word

15
00:00:27.966 --> 00:00:30.300
Xiao Can, do you know that because of this?

16
00:00:30.733 --> 00:00:33.000
Dad is already in the intensive care unit

17
00:00:33.866 --> 00:00:36.333
I beg you to raise your hand

18
00:00:36.333 --> 00:00:38.666
Let Jiangjiang have a way to live, okay?

19
00:00:38.700 --> 00:00:40.100
I've made it very clear

20
00:00:40.100 --> 00:00:41.166
The Jiang family has nothing to do with me

21
00:00:41.166 --> 00:00:42.566
You don't have to pester here

22
00:00:42.566 --> 00:00:44.033
Please go out

23
00:00:44.300 --> 00:00:45.100
Chen Huacan

24
00:00:45.400 --> 00:00:48.100
I always thought you were a knife with a mouth and a tofu heart

25
00:00:48.100 --> 00:00:49.766
I didn't expect you to be so cruel

26
00:00:49.766 --> 00:00:51.800
Halo Bank freezes our Jiangjia assets

27
00:00:51.800 --> 00:00:53.300
It must be your support.

28
00:00:53.300 --> 00:00:55.000
You just want revenge on the Zhang family

